list.abstract: annual（英 [ˈænjuəl]，美 [ˈænjuəl]），英语单词，作形容词用，意思为每年的；一年一度的；年度的。作名词时，为年鉴；年报；一年生植物。短语搭配有annual report（年度报告）。例句为“Our annual anniversary sales started on Monday.（我们一年一度的周年促销从星期一开始。）” annual形容词类近义词有yearly、etesian，名词类近义词有year book、almanac，相关反义词有biennial，副词形式为annually。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Stuart, I see you're getting ready for your Halloween party. Yeah, it's my annual attempt to meet women. Ninth time's the charm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯图尔特，你开始为万圣节派对做准备啦。这可是我每年的泡妞时节呢，希望第九次可以手到妞来。

yingyinNormal.en: MU's Greek Council. We sponsor the annual Scare Games.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怪大学生会，我们主办年度惊吓杯。

yingyinNormal.en: She won a thousand dollars. So this is an annual thing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 她为我们赢得了一千美元！啊，是一年一次的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: The what? It's an annual science conference. We've all been invited to speak.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？是一个年度科学会议，我们都被邀请发言。

yingyinNormal.en: 200 million Chinese leave the cities, the biggest annual migration of people on the planet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两亿国民离开城市，是规模最大的年度人口迁移，冠绝全球。

yingyinNormal.en: The Fifth Annual East Rutherford, New Jersey, Gay, Lesbian, Bisexual and Transgender Alliance Luau.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第五届新泽西州东卢瑟福德男同，女同，双性恋者和变性人联盟宴会。

yingyinNormal.en: To cope with a 30 million annual visitors, the Chinese have built the world's highest outdoor elevator.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了满足每年三千万人次的游客，中国修建了世界上最高的户外电梯。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I can breathe again. Babe, they want to have sex. Oh, of course! The annual birthday booty spectacular!
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，我又能呼吸了。亲爱的，他们想做爱。当然啊，年度生日庆祝打炮大典！

yingyinNormal.en: But one day, before the opening night of our school's annual musical, he walked up to me and holding a letter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是有一天在我们学校年度音乐会的前一个晚上，他走到我面前，拿着一封信。

yingyinNormal.en: Then the annual school fundraiser arrived and I found myself with a whole new set of problems. I was a Basketboy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 学校一年一度的筹款活动到了，我陷入一堆新难题。我要做篮子男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: Chuck's dad, Bart bass, is hosting the annual brunch for his foundation. Everyone is invited. Well, not everyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恰克的爸爸，巴特·拜斯，为他的基金会举办每年一度的早午餐会，所有人都得到邀请了，不是所有人。

yingyinNormal.en: I remember it distinctly because I had just composed my annual poem commemorating the anniversary of Dr. Seuss's death.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我记得非常清楚，因为当时我刚创作了一首年度诗歌，以在苏斯博士的逝世纪念日追忆他。

yingyinNormal.en: Simple binary pings on an annual basis give us some clue as to which worlds have potential. And one system shows promise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每年用简单的二进制方式进行分析我们得到了一些线索 哪些地方存在可能有一个很有希望的星系

yingyinNormal.en: Now that I'm no longer with Amy, I have an extra ticket to the annual Thanksgiving lunch buffet at the aquarium cafeteria. Who wants it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 鉴于我跟艾米已经分手了，我有多一张水族馆餐厅的年度感恩节自助午餐票，谁想要啊？
